Circular Dependency
===================

The two or more dependedncy which depend on each other.
A--> Depend on B
B-->Depend on A

This is the issue of Spring depeendency injection which bean need to inject first.

@Compomnent
public class Service A
{
    @Autowired
    public Service A{
    }

    @Autowired
    public Service B{
    }
}

@Autowired
@Lazy
public Service B{
}
